{"tid":632968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國前第一夫人芭芭拉逝世 享年92歲","createTime":"2018-04-18T01:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T06:14:26.000Z","uid":112702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7c53e08ca51a46899153f2e46d8f5bef0ffb43","tid":632968,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:37:19.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國前總統老布希（George H. W. Bush）的妻子芭芭拉（Barbara Bush）17日逝世，享耆壽92歲。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，老布希辦公室聲明透露芭芭拉的死訊，但葬禮時間尚未公布，也未公布死因。她的家人在15日曾表示，芭芭拉患有慢性阻塞性肺病和鬱血性心衰竭，身體相當虛弱，2017年初接受一連串的住院治療，最後她決定不再尋求治療，而是專注於「安撫護理」。<br />\n<br />\n芭芭拉曾在丈夫老布希就任美國第41任總統的1989年至1993年期間，擔任美國第一夫人。她的兒子小布希（George W. Bush）後來又在2000年的美國大選取得勝利，擔任美國第43任總統，就任期間為2001年至2009年。<br />\n<br />\n芭芭拉原本留有棕色頭髮，卻在1950年代開始轉白，她刻意不染髮，保留一頭白髮，變成美國人心目中的「全民奶奶」，她也因此被家人稱作「銀狐」。"},{"pid":"8994e3679d4f5f606ffe6f3748bddbea169e401c","tid":632968,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62cc57a0edbbb7c7af3cbb7ee3869eb73e37b71","tid":632968,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8994e3679d4f5f606ffe6f3748bddbea169e401c","tid":632968,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a9ae7fc9330645286367c0b1d649e1a308efea","tid":632968,"uid":135517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"f153cd44103006732f747ef6a0383b2a3e29538c","tid":632968,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"放棄治療, 放棄急救, 維持生命儀器<br />\n台灣已經立左法, 已經試驗推行中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港好似仲係要醫生批准<br />\n唔係病人之前決定便可"},{"pid":"19804c14ce087331deaef66ada0ed71b5d73dd9f","tid":632968,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97705b86f660503862332d300b61b913afbef35","tid":632968,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151219/36963378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20151219%2F36963378&d=ZchohgaxB9QG9V%2BAmERvXVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=23066ca9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20151219%2F36963378&h=c65f8f84\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151219/36963378</a><br />\n<br />\n《病人自主權利法》，民眾未來可先預立「醫療決定」，若病況符合末期病人、永久植物人、極重度失智等不可逆的昏迷，且經醫師、緩和醫療團隊確認病情不可逆，醫師可按預先擬好的醫療決定，選擇撤除維生器具、不灌食，讓民眾有「拒絕醫療」權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNo CPR Form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}